(112, 'Galgotias institute of management and technology', 'GIMT', 'gimt@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'galgotia_college1.jpg', 'gcet1.jpg', 'Galgotia , Knowledge Park I, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p><cite>GALGOTIAS INSTITUTE OF MANAGEMENT &amp; TECHNOLOGY</cite></p>\r\n\r\n<p>After being in the industry for more than five decades, Galgotias Educational Institutions are now synonymous with quality education. Under the visionary planning and dynamic leadership of Mr. Suneel Galgotia, Chairman, Galgotias Educational Institutions, the Galgotias institutions have carved a niche for themselves by producing professionals of national and international acclaim. Owing to its highly qualified faculty, state-of-the-art infrastructure, quality teaching and learning procedures, Galgotias institutions are emerging as the preferred institute for students opting for higher studies. It is the stringent check on quality that has made Galgotias institutions, the favourite destination for recruitment by renowned corporations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galgotias Educational Institutions (GEI) comprising of Galgotias Institute of Management &amp; Technology (GIMT), Galgotias College of Engineering &amp; Technology (GCET) have been founded by Smt. Shakuntala Educational &amp; Welfare Society. Mr. Suneel Galgotia, a resolute visionary, committed to providing world class technical and management education, is the Chairman. Galgotias Institute of Management &amp; Technology and Galgotias College of Engineering &amp; Technology are approved by AICTE, Ministry of HRD, Govt. of India. Affiliated to Uttar Pradesh Technical University, Lucknow, Galgotias College of Engineering &amp; Technology &amp; Galgotias Institute of Management &amp; Technology have acquired a unique status in the country by breaking new grounds is producing professionals of national and international acclaim and have been recognized among the top ranking institutions (Dataquest-Nasscom &rsquo;08 Survey, Outlook-C Fore and India Today Aspire).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG2119483921', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(113, 'GNIOT Group of Institutions', '', 'gniot@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'gniot.jpg', '', 'Plot No. 7, Knowledge Park II, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>About&nbsp;GNIOT</h1>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>About</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in the year 2001, GNIOT group of institutions has become one of the leading institutions for management and engineering programs worldwide. Our aim is to educate leaders who build a strong organization and wisely leverage the power of markets to create lasting value. The founders are some of the best minds from the corporate and academic worlds. In their perspective, the changing business landscape requires young leaders to have understanding of developing economies and global practices. GNIOT is committed to creating such leaders through its innovative programs, outstanding faculty and thought leadership. At GNIOT, we share a strong commitment to a diverse community. It&#39;s a commitment born out of our longstanding belief in the transforming power of a strong and collaborative organizational culture. We believe that leveraging diverse perspectives enriches learning, inspires innovation and develops strong leaders.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor us, diversity encompasses many dimensions &ndash; from personal characteristics to cultural traditions, political world views, academic training, life experiences and other aspects that shape human identity. At the core, all diversity matters. Differences affect how we think, react, create, problem solve and relate to others as people. Differences inform, enrich and empower humankind&#39;s collective capacity to create a better world &ndash; materially, aesthetically and philosophically. We welcome the vibrant array of cultures, voices and unique perspectives that together make GNIOT a dynamic place to learn, teach and thrive.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur students and learners along with our experienced faculty and administrators gets boundless opportunities to interact with experts from around the world and every imaginable background. We exchange knowledge with them not only in classrooms, but through seminars, meetings, club activities, conferences and global study trips. They forge lifelong bonds with others who share their intellectual curiosity and their desire to make a meaningful difference.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WHY GNIOT</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>S.NO</th>\r\n			<th>DESCRIPTION</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Started in 2001 with 2000 students, currently GNIOT has more than 6000 students in a lush and green huge campus.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>2</td>\r\n			<td>Best placement record in the region.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>3</td>\r\n			<td>GNIOT offers a programme in association with Reliance industries.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>4</td>\r\n			<td>GNIOT offers NCFM certification.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>5</td>\r\n			<td>ICICI Bank trains GNIOT students on finance related subjects.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>6</td>\r\n			<td>Only centre in Greater Noida for Prometric.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>7</td>\r\n			<td>CSR excellence award.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>8</td>\r\n			<td>More than 1.25 lakh books in the library.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>9</td>\r\n			<td>In house medical facilities.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>10</td>\r\n			<td>Digital interactive language lab for perfection in language skills.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>11</td>\r\n			<td>Largest residential campus-more than 700 girls and 1500+ boys currently staying.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>12</td>\r\n			<td>Association with IIT-Delhi and IIT-Mumbai for management training sessions.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>13</td>\r\n			<td>200+ faculties.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>14</td>\r\n			<td>10,000+ strong alumni base.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>15</td>\r\n			<td>Foreign exchange programme.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>16</td>\r\n			<td>Compulsory Summer Internship provided by the college.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>17</td>\r\n			<td>Nodal centre of IIT-Delhi and IIT-Mumbai.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>18</td>\r\n			<td><strong>36 corporate training programmes:</strong><br />\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Resonant Leadership</li>\r\n				<li>Workforce Management</li>\r\n				<li>Negotiation Skills</li>\r\n				<li>Stress Management</li>\r\n				<li>Evidence Based Competency Mapping</li>\r\n				<li>Emotional Intelligence</li>\r\n				<li>Crisis Action Preparedness and many more</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>19</td>\r\n			<td>Dual Specialization.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>20</td>\r\n			<td>Microsoft &amp; Oracle Certification programme.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>21</td>\r\n			<td>Certification in business skills.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>22</td>\r\n			<td>Certification in Telecom and Mobile communication.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>23</td>\r\n			<td>Industry vetted curriculum.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>24</td>\r\n			<td>Digital classrooms.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>25</td>\r\n			<td>Situational role plays.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>26</td>\r\n			<td>Management games.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>27</td>\r\n			<td><strong>Unique training and placement programmes which covers:</strong><br />\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Resume Making</li>\r\n				<li>Business Communication</li>\r\n				<li>Public Speaking</li>\r\n				<li>Negotiation Skills</li>\r\n				<li>Goal Achievers</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'CG781832827', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(114, 'Noida Institute of Engineering and Technology ', 'NIET', 'niet@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'niet.jpg', 'niet_lo.png', 'Noida Institute of Engineering & Technology, 19, Knowledge Park-II, Institutional Area, Greater Noida', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<h2>ABOUT INSTITUTE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>NIET is one of the premier Engineering and Management institutes of India&#39;s National Capital Region (NCR). It was established by eminent visionaries, responsible for setting up City Educational &amp; Social Welfare Society of Meerut, with a Vision to provide value driven education of global dimensions. The Institute is managed by City Educational &amp; Social Welfare Society, which runs several prestigious education and health organizations, viz. NIET (Noida Institute of Engineering &amp; Technology), MIET (Meerut Institute of Engineering &amp; Technology), CVPS (City Vocational Public School), ACTS C- DAC, Pyramid Finishing School, Dayanand Nursing Home, Chandra Sen Charitable Hospital &amp; Om Diagnostic Center. Noida Institute of Engineering and Technology, a self financed institute, offering high standard quality education to students from all corners of the country, is situated in Greater Noida (a hub of global MNCs.). The institute has a sprawling area of 13.90 acres and lush green ambiance all around. It is developing as the Center of Excellence imparting technical education and generating competent professionals with a high degree of credibility, integrity and ethical standards. We aim at recognizing, respecting and nurturing the creative potential of each student.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Institution Innovation Council-NIET</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Ministry of Human Resource Development (MHRD), Govt. of India has established &lsquo;MHRD&rsquo;s Innovation Cell (MIC)&rsquo; to systematically foster the culture of Innovation amongst all Higher Education Institutions (HEIs). The primary mandate of MIC is to encourage, inspire and nurture young students by supporting them to work with new ideas and transform them into prototypes while they are informative years. MIC has envisioned encouraging creation of &lsquo;Institution&rsquo;s Innovation Council (IICs)&rsquo; across selected HEIs. A network of these IICs will be established to promote innovation in the Institution through multitudinous modes leading to an innovation promotion eco-system in the campuses.</p>\r\n', 'CG1375749242', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(115, 'Lloyd Institute of Management and Technology', 'LLOYD-IMT', 'lloydimt@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'lloyd_colg.jpg', 'lloyd_logo1.png', 'Plot No: 11, Knowledge Park II, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p>Lloyd Institute of Management &amp; Technology&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&#39;The Department of Management, Lloyd Institute of Management and Technology (LIMT) is a part of the Lloyd Group of Institutions, Greater Noida. Since its inception, the Department of Management, LIMT, has created a nice for itself, in the academic corridors of higher professional education space in the country in general and Delhi/NCR in particular. The department imparts Masters Program in Management (MBA) from its earmarked campus, located at Knowledge Park II, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India.&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lloyd offers diploma&nbsp;undergraduate and postgraduate in the Department of Pharmacy. The institute also offers two year full-time MBA program which is affiliated to AKTU&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG623340065', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(116, 'LLoyd Law College', 'LLoyd,Law', 'lloydlc@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'lloyd_law.jpg', 'lloyd_logo2.png', ' Plot No. 11, Knowledge Park II, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Law', '', '<h2>Lloyd Law College</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Lloyd Law College is a premier educational institution offering legal education since year 2003 in affiliation with CCS University, Meerut, U.P. (state university established in 1965), and approved by the Bar Council of India (Statutory body for professional legal education in India).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College is blessed with the mentorship and patronage of Padma Shri Prof. (Dr.) N.R. Madhava Menon, &quot;The living legend of Law&quot; and the flag bearer of legal education reforms in India. Prof. Menon is a visionary of legal education who is also the designer and architect of the five-year integrated B.A.LL.B. Programme in India and the Founder of the premier legal institutions of the country including the National Law School of India University, Bangalore and the National University of Juridical Sciences, Kolkata. Prof. Menon&rsquo;s relentless efforts in revamping and modernizing the legal education of the country has successfully brought Indian legal education at par with the legal institutions in the developed countries.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1st</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>in UP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By CSR - GHRDC Law School Survey June 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3rd</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>College in North India</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By India Today</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4th</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>in India for the impact of research</p>\r\n', 'CG1868140375', 'accept', '', 'College');
