(143, 'SRM Institute Of Science & Technology (University)', 'SRM GZB', 'srmgzb@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '25-02-2020', 'srm_gzb.jpg', 'srm_gzb1.jpg', 'DELHI NCR CAMPUS, Modinagar, Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh 201204', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<p>Welcome to the world of<br />\r\nSRM INSTITUTE OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY, NCR Campus</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SRM</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Institute of Science &amp; Technology (Formally SRM University)</strong>&nbsp;is one of the top ranking deemed to be universities in India established under section 3 of the UGC Act 1956 with over 55000 students and 3000 faculty, offering a wide range of undergraduate, postgraduate and doctoral programs in Engineering, Management, Medicine and Health Sciences &amp; Science and Humanities spread over four campuses&nbsp;<strong>(Kattankulathur, Ramapuram, Vadapalani &amp; NCR &ndash; Ghaziabad)</strong>. The Institute is accredited with the top most &lsquo;A&rsquo; grade by the National Assessment and Accreditation Board of India (NAAC)&nbsp;<strong>and approved by&nbsp;<em>All India Council for Technical Education</em>&nbsp;(<em>AICTE</em>)</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SRM IST, Delhi NCR Campus, was established in the year 1997. The campus has more than 5000 students pursuing their career in Engineering, Management, and Hotel Management. More than 300 faculty members with excellent academic records.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The location of the campus is serene and provides environment for innovation and creativity. Spread across 27.14 acres of land, with lush green environment and good infrastructure like centralized library, well equipped technical labs, separate hostel facility for boys and girls, AC class rooms and Labs, with Wi-Fi connection around the campus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SRM IST is strongly committed to maintain the quality and excellence in education. The high quality of teaching, corporate consulting, management development and research is the hallmark of NCR Campus.</p>\r\n