INSERT INTO `offering` (`id`, `image`, `title1`, `title2`, `description`) VALUES
(4, 'rce_geospatialmarketing.jpg', 'RCE is offering world wide business planning. We are a solution oriented company and your needs are our greatest concern', 'GEOSPATIAL MARKETING', '<p>Geo-marketing is the integration of location based intelligence into various aspects of marketing, including sales, planning and distribution. Geographic parameters are used for marketing, research methodology for same including from sampling, data collection, analysis, and presentation are done keeping in mind these parameters. The design and planning stages of G.I.S development are crucial to success, both from a technical viewpoint and in terms of the cost efficiency of the entire scheme. Geo-Marketing Services include routing, territorial planning, and site selection etc.&nbsp;<br>Our expertise pivots on the analysis and documentation of user requirement and G.I.S ideals; with various organization scales in mind. Along with helping to \'spatially enable\' your existing computer applications. We carefully induct your people into the new system, as a part of a step-by-step orientation process. This process includes user workshops in data evaluation and analysis, cost/benefit analysis etc. Geo-information training, seminars and needs assessment are also offered under this section.</p>'),
(5, 'rce_training&workshop.jpg', 'RCE is offering world wide business planning. We are a solution oriented company and your needs are our greatest concern', 'TRAINING & WORKSHOP', '<p>In order to narrow the huge gap between demand and availability of G.I.S professionals, R.C.E. is keen to offer job oriented short term and long term training programs in G.I.S/ AutoCAD/ Arc Suite/ G.P.R/ E.P.L &amp; D.G.P.S/Total Station. These have been carefully constructed for industry needs and are handled by our industry experts with decades of experience.&nbsp;<br>R.C.E. imparts special training to students hence educating them to negotiate through the applied aspects of G.I.S and Remote Sensing and emerging real world problems of various kinds faced by the industries and the society on both the technological and environmental fronts.&nbsp;<br>R.C.E. is committed to provide and increase, awareness of G.I.S and its modeling tools for improving competition and business potential. We strive to develop a critical understanding of appropriate tools, exposure to new methods and techniques, gaining competence in developing tools for the acquisition, processing, transformation, analysis, modelling, storage and presentation of spatial data. Using geo-information in identifying and responding to development problems and in drafting development policies.</p><p><strong>Salient Features</strong></p><ul><li>To generate graphics, make them intelligent and structure data bases.</li><li>To plan, design, develop, implement, monitor, update and upgrade systems for G.I.S</li><li>To scan, capture, store, analyze and manage large collection of topographic maps, photographs, plans and engineering drawings etc. in digital form through to the creation of spatial databases.</li><li>To convert map data from raster to vector, between different formats and the Indian.</li><li>National Standard format of Survey of India, from one projection to the other and even from one Geodetic Datum to the other.</li><li>Digital Terrain Modelling in 3-D, spatial analysis and production.</li><li>Digital Data Generation through Mass Digitization using scanners, doing screen digitization using SemiÂ­ automatic digital techniques and photogrammetric techniques.</li><li>Digital Data Integration, Warping, Edge Matching, Updating and Overlaying Capabilities.</li><li>To carry out geospatial product generation for standard, value added derivative and specialized Digital Cartographic Products.</li><li>Geo-Database Structuring, Modification and Access capabilities.</li><li>Modernization of Cadastra and Computerization of land records using digital techniques.</li><li>G.I.S Mapping and Ground Surveys for Land use planning for urban area specially for municipalities using GPS in DGPS mode and Total Stations.</li><li>G.I.S Mapping and Ground Surveys for towns, tunnel alignment, canals, pipelines, Power Transmission Lines and for Feasibility Studies for roads, express highways and National Highways.</li><li>Digital Data Generation through Mass Digitization using scanners, doing screen digitization using SemiÂ­ automatic digital techniques and photogrammetric techniques.</li><li>Integration and updating with Aerial Photographs and satellite based SPOT, TM, IRS- IC, IKONOS, Quick bird Data specially for urban development.</li><li>Networking and communication set up.</li><li>Consultancy Services for any of the above operations. Site Development and System Procurement Services.</li><li>Cartographic Work, G.I.S Application Development including Land Base Data Model and Electrical Networking G.I.S</li><li>Offering Cartographic Services for Global Street Mapping.</li><li>Roads and village Geo Database for India.</li></ul><p>On completion of the course, participants are able to:</p><ul><li>Analyze geo-information problems encountered in professional practice and develop appropriate methods for studying and/or solving the problems.</li><li>Apply appropriate methods for collecting, acquiring and verifying spatial data.</li><li>Use geo-information science and earth observation technology to generate, integrate, analyse and visualise spatial data.</li><li>Evaluate and apply relevant and appropriate methods and models for data analysis and problem solving.</li><li>Apply practical skills to carry out an independent final assignment (pilot project).</li><li>All this is under the umbrella of â€œRidings Institute of Geomaticsâ€ registered in Uttrakhand, India. We have provided training to 120 Engineers successfully.</li></ul>'),
(6, 'rce_ridings_strength.jpg', 'RCE is offering world wide business planning. We are a solution oriented company and your needs are our greatest concern', 'RIDINGâ€™S STRENGTH', '<ul><li>Quality and Accuracy - As per Survey of India and Industry Standard Norms.</li><li>Employing Ex. Survey of India Experienced Specialists and can offer InÂ­ House Consultancy.</li><li>Best Ground Survey and Map Generation Expertise through Survey of India Ex officers and Professional.</li><li>State of the Art Survey Instruments like G.P.S, D.G.P.S, G.P.R, S.E.B.A Locator, Total Stations, Disto Meter and other Mapping Equipment.</li><li>Successfully Done Property &amp; Consumer Survey Project Government and Private Organization India and Abroad.</li><li>RCE-I always follows S.O.I. working procedures and norms.</li><li>RCE-I Is Fully Conversant with Datum, Projections etc.</li><li>Leading company in S.U.E survey and have completed more than 13000 km survey.</li><li>Own 14 GSSi make G.P.R machine &amp; have in house team of experience geophysicist.</li></ul>');
INSERT INTO `overview` (`id`, `description`) VALUES
(1, '<p>RIDINGS CONSULTING ENGINEERS INDIA LTD (R.C.E.) is a company at the leading edge of technology, providing an entire range of services in the field of surveying, mapping and Geospatial Services. The company was founded in 1995&nbsp;by (Late) Mr.&nbsp;S.D. Baveja with an aim to provide G.I.S. solutions and generate employment for this sector. Up until early this year, the activities of Ridings were being guided by its founder/promoter (Late) Mr. S. D. Baveja, who retired from the Survey of India as National Project Director of Modern Cartographic Centre (UNDP Project) and Digital Mapping Centre, after over 38 years of service.</p><p>Today Ridings Consulting Engineers India Limited is a more than 2 decades old entity and a BSE Listed Company (BSE SME Exchange). The Company since the very beginning has been operating on its motto i.e. Global Thinking and Universal Outlook, as a result of which Ridings has become a well-known brand associated with top Indian Companies. The Company in recent years has grown its clientage and worked in geographically enhanced areas executing various projects in the Middle East region and has entered North Africa. R.C.E. is certified ISO 9001:2015 organization and its production headquarter is located in Noida, India.</p><p>We always remain at the leading edge of technology providing an entire range of services in the field of Underground Survey, by using Ground Penetrating Radar (GPR), Geospatial data creation services using Remote Sensing &amp; Satellite image, Topographical Surveying and engineering services and GIS Trunkey Solutions both at National and International Level.</p><p>The Company has a wide arsenal of state of the art technology for Underground surveys, digital mapping, GIS-related applications, geophysical mapping and other geospatial services. Besides this the Company has a number of specialized and trained geophysicist in its employment to cater to any size of geophysical survey project at any given point of time and is probably the largest company in India using this Green, nondestructive technology.</p><p>The Companyâ€™s management at present is working with guidance of Mr. Praveen Kumar Baveja, Whole time Director &amp; Chief Executive Officer, of the Company who holds a degree of Master of Technology from IIT, Kharagpur and comes with an experience of more than 35 years on the Board of the Company. He is being aptly supported by Mr. Sudhir Kumar Baveja, who also heads the finance department as the Chief Financial Officer, he has an experience of more than 25 years in the field of finance with reputed multinational companies and holds the degree of prestige Cost and Work Accountant from I.C.W.A.. In addition to this, the company has reputed 2 non- executive Independent Directors.</p>');
